{"title":"Kogel Spins Oversized Ceramic-Bearing Pulleys for SRAM T-Type","link":"https://bikerumor.com/kogel-spins-oversized-ceramic-bearing-pulleys-for-sram-t-type/","date":1704472398000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1155\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1.jpg\" alt=\"kogel upper derailleur pulley with ceramic bearings for SRAM Transmission\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1-297x214.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1-800x578.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1-120x87.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1-768x554.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-1-1536x1109.jpg 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Kogel’s latest ceramic bearing pulleys give SRAM Transmission riders a bigger, more colorful option for modding their rear derailleur.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The alloy pulleys use the stock cage on GX, X0, XX and XXSL Transmission derailleurs, but increase the lower pulley tooth count to 18, up from SRAM’s stock 16-tooth unit. The upper pulley remains at 14 teeth, same as stock. Kogel says there’s no need to lengthen your chain with that small of an increase.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2.jpg\"><img width=\"1340\" height=\"1845\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2.jpg\" alt=\"kogel ceramic bearing derailleur pulleys for SRAM Transmission\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2.jpg 1340w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2-218x300.jpg 218w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2-800x1101.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2-87x120.jpg 87w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2-768x1057.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-2-1116x1536.jpg 1116w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Available in six colors (black, blue, red, gold, raw, and purple), they retail for <strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=19689&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kogel.cc%2Fproducts%2F14-18t-oversized-derailleur-pulleys-for-sram-transmission\">$199.99</a></strong> for the set.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3.jpg\"><img width=\"823\" height=\"660\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3.jpg\" alt=\"six color options for kogel ceramic bearing derailleur pulleys for SRAM Transmission\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3.jpg 823w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3-297x238.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3-800x642.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3-120x96.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kogel-transmission-ceramic-pulleys-3-768x616.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pair these pulleys with their recent <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kogel-gain-chains-come-pre-waxed-for-easy-speed/\">pre-waxed chain</a> for maximum friction reduction, and keep an eye out for bundle deals…Kogel frequently has discounts when you buy a bottom bracket with pulleys or their Kolossos oversized pulley cage.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=19689&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kogel.cc%2Fproducts%2F14-18t-oversized-derailleur-pulleys-for-sram-transmission\" target=\"_blank\">Kogel.cc</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/kogel-spins-oversized-ceramic-bearing-pulleys-for-sram-t-type/\">Kogel Spins Oversized Ceramic-Bearing Pulleys for SRAM T-Type</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"053c1bba84d5b00add10e779e407a05362f1ba983a34fb9ae7b846752cb16898","category":"Cycling"}